'''中古突厥语'''<ref>{{cite book|author=Yusuf Has Hacib|title=Kutadğu Bilig|translator=Mustafa S. Kaçalin|publisher=T. C. Kültür ve Turizm Bakanlığı Kütüphaneler ve Yayımlar Genel Mudürlüğü|page=3|ISBN=978-975-17-3359-7}}</ref>指[[突厥语族|突厥语族]]语言的一个演化阶段，覆盖了大部分[[中世纪|中世纪]]（公元900–1500年）。这个术语被用来代指一个包含[[葛逻禄语支|葛逻禄语支]]和[[乌古斯语支|乌古斯语支]]和相关语言的位于[[中亚|中亚]]、[[伊朗|伊朗]]和[[中东|中东]][[塞尔柱王朝|塞尔柱王朝]]占领区的其余部分一个语言群。其最广为人知的书面形式是位于[[喀什市|喀什市]]、[[八剌沙衮|八剌沙衮]]和[[丝绸之路|丝绸之路]]沿线其他城市的[[喀喇汗国|喀喇汗国]]<ref name="Norton1995">{{cite book|author=Mary Beth Norton|title=The American Historical Association's guide to historical literature|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=a0zgAAAAMAAJ&q=Qarakhanid+etc|year=1995|publisher=Oxford University Press|page=260|isbn=9780195057270|access-date=2021-04-07|archive-date=2021-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211030230633/https://books.google.com/books?id=a0zgAAAAMAAJ&q=Qarakhanid+etc}}</ref><ref name="Golden2010">{{cite book|author=Peter B. Golden|title=Turks and Khazars: Origins, Institutions, and Interactions in Pre-Mongol Eurasia|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=AOhIAQAAIAAJ&q=yalnguq+Uyghur+Oghuz+|year=2010|publisher=Ashgate/Variorum|isbn=978-1-4094-0003-5|page=104|access-date=2021-04-07|archive-date=2021-10-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211030230550/https://books.google.com/books?id=AOhIAQAAIAAJ&q=yalnguq+Uyghur+Oghuz+}}</ref>（也称喀喇汗突厥语）<ref>Bill Hickman, Gary Leiser, （2015）, ''Turkish Language, Literature, and History. Travelers' Tales, Sultans, and Scholars Since the Eighth Century'', p. 139</ref>方言。[[察合台汗国|察合台汗国]]书面语可能是中古突厥语的晚期形式。但令人困惑的是葛逻禄和乌古斯的“中古突厥语”时期与8至13世纪的东突厥的[[古代突厥语|古代突厥语]]时期重叠。

